                    <span>Just responding to a mistake by another reviewer. This book comes with an unmodified stock version of Torque, specifically version 1.2, downloaded from CVS on January 10, 2004. If you buy a Torque license (cost $100), you will be able to download that old version of the Torque source.
<br />
